casebody.data:
Marta Maria BASCOY, et al., Appellant(s)/petitioner(s),
v.
DEPARTMENT OF BUSINESS AND PROFESSIONAL REGULATION, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-0923, 3D17-0911 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017

ORDERED that appellants' notice of dismissal is recognized by the Court, and these consolidated administrative appeals from the Department of Business and Professional Regulation are hereby dismissed.
